rows.label: qst001603_msg0001
rows.name:
Thanks a million. I may have gone
a little overboard with the requests...

rows.label: qst001603_msg0002
rows.name:
Well, I'd better get to work on the new
menu.

rows.label: qst001603_msg0003
rows.name: You get first bite again. So stick around!

rows.label: qst001603_msg0004
rows.name: これが新作料理名（仮）だ！

rows.label: qst001603_msg0006
rows.name: Yup. None too shabby, is it?

rows.label: qst001603_msg0007
rows.name:
The new menu's complete now. Thanks
to your help!

rows.label: qst001603_msg0008
rows.name: I'd better give you your reward.

rows.label: qst001603_msg0009
rows.name:
Ah, money's not really enough for all
that you've done for me! So, I've
thought up a new recipe, just for you.

rows.label: qst001603_msg0011
rows.name:
Price notwithstanding, I'd say it's the
tastiest morsel you'll get in the whole
of Superbia!

rows.label: qst001603_msg0012
rows.name:
Maybe if there's a budding chef
amongst you, you can have them
whip it up!

rows.label: qst001603_msg0013
rows.name: Honestly, the taste is to die for.

rows.label: qst001603_msg0014
rows.name:
No, no! All the thanks should be going
in your direction! Well, see you around!
